description: The serial number of the server hardware in CZJ9260730, bay 5 matches the serial number of the server hardware originally used to create this server profile but the server hardware type is different. The server hardware type is "SY 480 Gen10 2" but the expected server hardware type is "SY 480 Gen10 1".

eventDetails.eventItemValue: Perform one of the following: Replace the server hardware with its original hardware configuration in CZJ9260730, bay 1, or edit the server profile and select different server hardware, server hardware type and/or enclosure group.
